1405
01:26:05.827 --> 01:26:07.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
But, uh,

1406
01:26:07.745 --> 01:26:10.540 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
