1410
01:26:22.969 --> 01:26:27.599 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Elliott had a very strong</i>
<i>militaristic kind of approach to life.</i>

1411
01:26:27.682 --> 01:26:29.100 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
