1416
01:26:48.578 --> 01:26:50.788 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Brenda] <i>Eddy said he always</i>
<i>sort of didn't feel like</i>

1417
01:26:50.872 --> 01:26:53.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>he fit in with his family.</i>

1418
01:26:57.086 --> 01:26:58.588 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>He always felt like...</i>

1419
01:26:59.339 --> 01:27:01.466 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Like he wasn't in the right place.

1420
01:27:07.347 --> 01:27:08.723 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[interviewer]
<i>How much did you have any sense</i>

1421
01:27:08.806 --> 01:27:10.350 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
that Edward was unhappy?

1422
01:27:12.560 --> 01:27:15.313 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
