1423
01:27:21.653 --> 01:27:24.030 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>We were a rather quiet family.</i>

1424
01:27:24.364 --> 01:27:28.576 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>We didn't tell our problems</i>
<i>to one another.</i>

1425
01:27:31.204 --> 01:27:33.081 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
We protected each other.

1426
01:27:33.164 --> 01:27:35.667 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
It was a nice family.

1427
01:27:41.506 --> 01:27:44.008 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Some people are just not a good fit.

1428
01:27:49.347 --> 01:27:51.808 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>It wasn't his father's fault.</i>

1429
01:27:52.684 --> 01:27:57.355 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Elliott did what he believed</i>
<i>to be best as a parent.</i>

1430
01:27:58.731 --> 01:28:00.358 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>They were just different people.</i>

1431
01:28:02.151 --> 01:28:05.822 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I got the phone call from...
