1432
01:28:06.906 --> 01:28:09.409 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
And he told me to sit down.

1433
01:28:11.286 --> 01:28:13.371 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
And I said, "No need to."

1434
01:28:14.122 --> 01:28:16.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
And he told me about it.

1435
01:28:17.750 --> 01:28:19.085 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
And then,

1436
01:28:20.461 --> 01:28:22.171 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
standing right there,

1437
01:28:23.006 --> 01:28:24.841 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I went over to my wife

1438
01:28:26.301 --> 01:28:30.054 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
