1439
01:28:31.347 --> 01:28:35.226 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
And we stood there
for quite a while, crying.

1440
01:28:40.732 --> 01:28:41.816 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
And...

1441
01:28:45.194 --> 01:28:46.654 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
That was it.

1442
01:28:59.459 --> 01:29:02.962 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>I often wondered whether</i>
<i>I didn't teach him something.</i>

1443
01:29:07.050 --> 01:29:09.218 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Because of the way he left.

1444
01:29:11.929 --> 01:29:15.391 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I don't know.
Maybe I didn't teach him something.

1445
01:29:16.601 --> 01:29:19.395 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
How to live life or something.

1446
01:29:19.937 --> 01:29:22.106 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
That bothers me occasionally.

1447
01:29:33.951 --> 01:29:37.455 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Cervone]<i> Why did the boys' lives</i>
<i>turn out completely different?</i>

1448
01:29:38.748 --> 01:29:40.124 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>I don't need to read any books.</i>

1449
01:29:40.249 --> 01:29:41.959 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>I don't need to read any studies.</i>

1450
01:29:44.045 --> 01:29:47.590 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>I saw it firsthand with those three boys.</i>

1451
01:29:51.427 --> 01:29:53.096 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
It's all about nurture.

1452
01:30:04.941 --> 01:30:06.651 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[audience applauding]

1453
01:30:07.568 --> 01:30:09.278 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
These three young men,

1454
01:30:09.362 --> 01:30:11.614 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
they're all seated in the same position.

1455
01:30:11.697 --> 01:30:12.698 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[audience laughs]

1456
01:30:12.782 --> 01:30:14.742 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
