1457
01:30:14.826 --> 01:30:17.203 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>because that's what people</i>
<i>were looking for.</i>

1458
01:30:17.411 --> 01:30:19.205 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
They smoke the same kind of cigarettes.

1459
01:30:19.288 --> 01:30:20.456 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You say, "Oh, my God!

1460
01:30:20.540 --> 01:30:23.042 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
They're smoking Marlboros.
That's amazing!"

1461
01:30:23.126 --> 01:30:25.211 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
What you're not looking for
are their differences.

1462
01:30:25.294 --> 01:30:27.421 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I can't get over it, I'm telling you.

1463
01:30:27.505 --> 01:30:29.382 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-You all wrestled at one time?
-[together] Yes.

1464
01:30:29.924 --> 01:30:32.885 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
We found the ways that we were alike,

1465
01:30:32.969 --> 01:30:36.055 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
and we emphasized them,
and we wanted to be alike.

1466
01:30:37.765 --> 01:30:39.809 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>We were falling in love with each other.</i>

1467
01:30:40.852 --> 01:30:43.771 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Brenda]
<i>I think there were superficialities.</i>

1468
01:30:44.480 --> 01:30:48.192 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>They liked the same things,</i>
<i>and they had similar interests,</i>

1469
01:30:48.276 --> 01:30:50.987 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
