1471
01:31:02.915 --> 01:31:04.792 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Wright] <i>I've come to believe</i>

1472
01:31:05.293 --> 01:31:07.753 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>genes and the environment are...</i>

1473
01:31:08.671 --> 01:31:10.214 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Close competitors.

1474
01:31:12.800 --> 01:31:15.887 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>You could say that</i>
<i>we drift in the direction</i>

1475
01:31:15.970 --> 01:31:18.556 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>that our genes tell us to go.</i>

1476
01:31:19.849 --> 01:31:21.225 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>But it doesn't mean</i>

1477
01:31:21.309 --> 01:31:25.396 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
