1479
01:31:34.614 --> 01:31:37.533 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>because of the foundation</i>
<i>that was given to me by my parents.</i>

1480
01:31:38.951 --> 01:31:40.328 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>I believe that</i>

1481
01:31:40.828 --> 01:31:43.372 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
absolutely made the difference

1482
01:31:43.664 --> 01:31:46.918 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
in terms of struggling with
whatever demons I struggle with.

1483
01:31:49.837 --> 01:31:54.425 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Page] <i>I believe nature</i>
<i>and nurture both matter.</i>

1484
01:31:55.551 --> 01:31:58.721 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
But I think nurture

1485
01:31:58.971 --> 01:32:02.642 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
can overcome nearly everything.

1486
01:32:38.010 --> 01:32:39.845 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Wright] <i>Because the study's</i>
<i>never been published,</i>

1487
01:32:39.929 --> 01:32:41.806 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>we simply don't know definitively</i>

1488
01:32:41.889 --> 01:32:44.850 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
how many people's lives
were separated in this fashion.

1489
01:32:45.935 --> 01:32:49.313 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
