1490
01:32:51.899 --> 01:32:55.569 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
There's probably at least four individuals

1491
01:32:55.653 --> 01:32:57.989 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
who were subjects in this study

1492
01:32:58.072 --> 01:33:00.741 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
