1493
01:33:02.118 --> 01:33:05.079 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
If they know
that there are still twins out there

1494
01:33:05.371 --> 01:33:08.207 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
