1495
01:33:08.291 --> 01:33:10.418 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
It boggles the mind.

1496
01:33:10.751 --> 01:33:12.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
There's two ways of thinking about it.

1497
01:33:13.004 --> 01:33:16.132 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
These people really should know
