1498
01:33:16.215 --> 01:33:17.466 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Or, oh, my God,

1499
01:33:17.550 --> 01:33:19.510 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
