1503
01:33:31.689 --> 01:33:33.899 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
It really opens up the possibility

1504
01:33:33.983 --> 01:33:36.736 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
